column4: <content>1 zwart/wit foto: Cat. tent. Jan van Scorel, Centraal Museum Utrecht. The Tower reaches into the clouds! Port on right! Bottom: The Prophet? Isaiah? Jeremiah? This is not Nimrod's tower, but the story of the confusion of languages; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. After Patenier's lost picture in Venice, at least partly.'</content>
<part_of.title>Towers of Babel. Reproductions. Towers of Babel by other Artists.</part_of.title>
